w:<br>[1] Tap the &quot;Summon&quot; icon at the bottom of the main screen[2] Tap the &quot;Showcase Info&quot; button in the center right side of the screen[3] Tap the &quot;Details&quot; tab at the top of the Showcase Info screen</div><div>9. The summon showcase schedule and content may change without warning.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1543471200,update_time1543558335